do not regard them.”"},{"kind":"text","text":" He disregarded his brothers"},{"kind":"text","text":" and didn’t acknowledge his sons,"},{"kind":"text","text":" for they kept your word"},{"kind":"text","text":" and maintained your covenant. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:25–29","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":25,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 32:25–29","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will teach your ordinances to Jacob"},{"kind":"text","text":" and your instruction to Israel; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 31:9","book":"Deu","chapter":31,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" they will set incense before you"},{"kind":"text","text":" and whole burnt offerings on your altar."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 31:9","book":"Deu","chapter":31,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", bless his possessions, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or abilities"},{"kind":"text","text":" and accept the work of his hands."},{"kind":"text","text":" Break the back "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or waist"},{"kind":"text","text":" of his adversaries and enemies,"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that they cannot rise again."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or abilities"},{"marker":1,"text":"Or waist"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Benjamin:"},{"kind":"text","text":" The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s beloved rests "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Let the Lord’s beloved rest"},{"kind":"text","text":" securely on him."},{"kind":"text","text":" He "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads The Most High"},{"kind":"text","text":" shields him all day long,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he rests on his shoulders. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or and he dwells among his mountain slopes"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Let the Lord’s beloved rest"},{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads The Most High"},{"marker":1,"text":"Or and he dwells among his mountain slopes"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Joseph:"},{"kind":"text","text":" May his land be blessed by the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the dew of heaven’s bounty"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the watery depths that lie beneath; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 3:20","book":"Pro","chapter":3,"verse":20,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 3:20","book":"Pro","chapter":3,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"with the bountiful harvest from the sun"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the abundant yield of the seasons;"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"with the best products of the ancient mountains"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the bounty of the eternal hills; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 49:26","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 3:6","book":"Hab","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 49:26","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":26},{"label":"Hab 3:6","book":"Hab","chapter":3,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"with the choice gifts of the land"},{"kind":"text","text":" and everything in it;"},{"kind":"text","text":" and with the favor of him"},{"kind":"text","text":" who appeared "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit dwelt"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the burning bush. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:2–4","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" May these rest on the head of Joseph,"},{"kind":"text","text":" on the brow of the prince of his brothers. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 49:26","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":26,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:2–4","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":2},{"label":"Gn 49:26","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit dwelt"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"His firstborn bull has "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some DSS, Sam, LXX, Syr, Vg read A firstborn bull —he has"},{"kind":"text","text":" splendor,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and horns like "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit and his horns are"},{"kind":"text","text":" those of a wild ox;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he gores all the peoples with them"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the ends of the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":" Such are the ten thousands of Ephraim,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and such are the thousands of Manasseh."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some DSS, Sam, LXX, Syr, Vg read A firstborn bull —he has"},{"marker":1,"text":"Lit and his horns are"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Zebulun:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Rejoice, Zebulun, in your journeys,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Issachar, in your tents."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They summon the peoples to a mountain;"},{"kind":"text","text":" there they offer acceptable sacrifices."},{"kind":"text","text":" For they draw from the wealth of the seas"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the hidden treasures of the sand. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 49:13","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 5:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 5:18","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 49:13","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":13},{"label":"Jdg 5:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":15},{"label":"Jdg 5:18","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Gad:"},{"kind":"text","text":" The one who enlarges Gad’s territory"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be blessed."},{"kind":"text","text":" He lies down like a lion"},{"kind":"text","text":" and tears off an arm or even a head. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 12:8","book":"1Ch","chapter":12,"verse":8,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 12:8","book":"1Ch","chapter":12,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He chose the best part for himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":" because a ruler’s portion was assigned there for him."},{"kind":"text","text":" He came with the leaders of the people;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he carried out the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s justice"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his ordinances for Israel. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 32:1","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":1,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 32:1","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Dan:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Dan is a young lion,"},{"kind":"text","text":" leaping out of Bashan. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 5:17","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":17,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 5:17","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Naphtali:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Naphtali, enjoying approval,"},{"kind":"text","text":" full of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s blessing,"},{"kind":"text","text":" take "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX, Syr, Vg, Tg read he will take"},{"kind":"text","text":" possession to the west and the south."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX, Syr, Vg, Tg read he will take"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said about Asher:"},{"kind":"text","text":" May Asher "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Happy or Blessed; Gn 30:13"},{"kind":"text","text":" be the most blessed of the sons;"},{"kind":"text","text":" may he be the most favored among his brothers"},{"kind":"text","text":" and dip his foot in olive oil. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 49:20","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":20,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 49:20","book":"Gen","chapter":49,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Happy or Blessed; Gn 30:13"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"May the bolts of your gate be iron and bronze,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and your strength last as long as you live."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There is none like the God of Jeshurun,"},{"kind":"text","text":" who rides the heavens to your aid,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the clouds in his majesty. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 22:8","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 18:7–19","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 68:4","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 68:33","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":33,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 19:1","book":"Isa","chapter":19,"verse":1,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Sm 22:8","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 18:7–19","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":7},{"label":"Ps 68:4","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":4},{"label":"Ps 68:33","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":33},{"label":"Is 19:1","book":"Isa","chapter":19,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The God of old is your dwelling place, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 91:9","book":"Psa","chapter":91,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and underneath are the everlasting arms."},{"kind":"text","text":" He drives out the enemy before you"},{"kind":"text","text":" and commands, “Destroy!”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 91:9","book":"Psa","chapter":91,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Israel dwells securely; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 25:18","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:5","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 12:10","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 33:12","book":"Deu","chapter":33,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:6","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 33:16","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 28:26","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":26,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":28,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 39:6","book":"Ezk","chapter":39,"verse":6,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jacob lives untroubled "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Text emended; MT reads Jacob’s fountain is alone"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:9","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in a land of grain and new wine;"},{"kind":"text","text":" even his skies drip with dew. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 8:7","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":7,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 25:18","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":18},{"label":"Lv 26:5","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":5},{"label":"Dt 12:10","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":10},{"label":"Dt 33:12","book":"Deu","chapter":33,"verse":12},{"label":"Jr 23:6","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":6},{"label":"Jr 33:16","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":16},{"label":"Ezk 28:26","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":26},{"label":"Ezk 34:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":28},{"label":"Ezk 39:6","book":"Ezk","chapter":39,"verse":6},{"label":"Nm 23:9","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":9},{"label":"Dt 8:7","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Text emended; MT reads Jacob’s fountain is alone"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:33:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"How happy you are, Israel!"},{"kind":"text","text":" Who is like you,"},{"kind":"text","text":" a people saved by the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"},{"kind":"text","text":" He is the shield that protects you,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the sword you boast in."},{"kind":"text","text":" Your enemies will cringe before you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 22:44","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":44,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 18:43–45","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":43,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and you will tread on their backs. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or high places"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:13","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 3:19","book":"Hab","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Sm 22:44","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":44},{"label":"Ps 18:43–45","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":43},{"label":"Dt 32:13","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":13},{"label":"Hab 3:19","book":"Hab","chapter":3,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or high places"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279366516}